{"tid":2255880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"潘媽媽稱昨晚警方只是聯絡提及交還洗黑錢案中女兒證物","createTime":"2020-10-24T02:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T04:08:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70aa01bfb13b14e90ced6ee965b2c00dac6c418b","tid":2255880,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"台灣殺人案疑犯陳同佳已出獄一年，仍未到台灣投案。對於警方表示已致電案中死者潘曉穎的母親、以了解事件最新情況，潘曉穎母親透過中間人回覆傳媒查詢時表示，警方當時只是聯絡她提及交還涉及洗黑錢案中女兒的證物。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，昨天晚上9時接獲電話，但內容並非關於她近日所提希望當中間人，邀請本港警方與台灣警方坐下商討的事，她仍希望本港警方就此事盡快跟她聯絡。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556461-20201024.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556461-20201024.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=c19cb190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556461-20201024.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f1e5eec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556461-20201024.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f2cf8da4b633d8bf78833f076769a93f2c2143aa","tid":2255880,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T02:38:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c814d00a48303d23b0072e0898f3d82c3692a97","tid":2255880,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"佳仔份認罪口供呢"},{"pid":"ec502f1c50ce115e22d6ba33df5ffca8dd987883","tid":2255880,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"潘老母你自己去殺陳同街報私仇啦！你日撚日都走出嚟老是常出現！！真係好撚煩！！全世界得你一個人死左個女咩！？個個都話要報仇仲得了！？上年至今死左嘅手足嘅私怨係咪搵你報！？"},{"pid":"60956d3a89f382bdf0c2a30768b53853687205e7","tid":2255880,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2cf8da4b633d8bf78833f076769a93f2c2143aa","tid":2255880,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime